name: Jesse Carere
introduction: 17, is from Woodbridge, ON. His parents are Milva and Vince Carere and he is the eldest of three siblings. Jesse currently attends St. Michael’s College School in downtown Toronto. He loves cinema and his favorite hobby is watching a good movie. His favorite actors are Johnny Depp, Leonardo DiCaprio, Matt Damon, and Robert Downey. Jr. Jesse’s interest in acting led to his very first role as Chris in MTV’s version of Skins. He has always lived by the saying, “Shoot for the moon. Even if you miss it, you’ll land among the stars”. He is very honored to be associated with such an amazing cast.
